771
00:54:00,920 --> 00:54:04,880
She was all messed up. Couldn't
tell what she was gonna do next.

772
00:54:04,960 --> 00:54:07,320
I didn't know this
was gonna happen.

773
00:54:07,400 --> 00:54:10,760
