864
01:00:14,400 --> 01:00:16,440
Well, her brother's up
at Walkerton Work Camp.

865
01:00:16,560 --> 01:00:20,560
Now, if you could get him a visit with her,
that would mean a lot.

866
01:00:20,640 --> 01:00:24,000
- I'll see what I can do.
- Well, that'd be great.

867
01:00:24,080 --> 01:00:26,200
- See y'all.
- Bye, Rick.

868
01:00:42,760 --> 01:00:45,720
- Hey, how's it goin'?
