870
01:00:48,160 --> 01:00:50,440
- Shit!
- This came this morning.

871
01:00:50,520 --> 01:00:53,040
- No hearing, nothing. Just a ruling.
- Man.

872
01:00:53,120 --> 01:00:57,400
Our next move should be Judge Gorman
on the Federal Court of Appeals.
He's a good guy.

873
01:00:57,520 --> 01:00:59,400
