875
01:01:02,800 --> 01:01:06,920
Look, uh, you should know I left the job.
I have no authority any more.

876
01:01:07,000 --> 01:01:11,280
Well, great. Now that you're no longer a
third-rate bureaucrat, you can really help.

877
01:01:11,360 --> 01:01:13,560
Well, let's hope so.

878
01:01:15,160 --> 01:01:18,120
Mrs Gorman, I promise you I would not be
calling you at your home at this hour...

879
01:01:18,240 --> 01:01:20,120
if it weren't urgent.

880
01:01:20,240 --> 01:01:23,840
No, l-I understand. It's-It's...
It's his vacation, but...

881
01:01:23,960 --> 01:01:27,320
Well... No, I'm...
I'm sorry, but...

882
01:01:27,440 --> 01:01:29,480
Well, all right.

883
01:01:29,600 --> 01:01:32,960
Uh, look, I'm sorry
to have bothered you.

884
01:01:34,240 --> 01:01:37,120
- Hi.
- Remember me?

885
01:01:37,240 --> 01:01:39,600
I've got a fully-stocked bar now.

886
01:01:41,920 --> 01:01:45,120
Uh, this is for you.

887
01:01:45,240 --> 01:01:47,280
He's a family friend...

888
01:01:47,360 --> 01:01:50,800
and, uh, I guess
you'll be lookin' for a job.

889
01:01:53,240 --> 01:01:57,920
- Senator Paul Hagan?
- He's looking for a new legislative aide.

890
01:01:58,000 --> 01:02:00,600
